Package: messentials
Title: Essential Functions for Data Wrangling
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Windisch", email = "michael.windisch@unido.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Currently contains two functions: suma(), an alternative version of sum(x, na.rm = T) and fct_combineall(), a function that makes it easier to add "Totals" for data at different factor levels.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
Imports: dplyr, forcats, magrittr, rlang
License: open
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
